org.freehep.graphics2d

Interface VectorGraphicsConstants

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPSGraphics2D, AbstractVectorGraphics, AbstractVectorGraphicsIO, DummyGraphics2D, EMFGraphics2D, EPSGraphics2D, GIFGraphics2D, ImageGraphics2D, JAVAGraphics2D, PDFGraphics2D, PixelGraphics2D, PSGraphics2D, SVGGraphics2D, SWFGraphics2D, TestAll, TestPerformance, TestPreviewThumbnail, TestSymbols2D, VectorGraphics, VectorGraphicsIO

    public interface VectorGraphicsConstants
    This interface defines useful constants for users of the VectorGraphics interface.
    Version:
    $Id: freehep-graphics2d/src/main/java/org/freehep/graphics2d/VectorGraphicsConstants.java 7aee336a8992 2005/11/25 23:19:05 duns $
    Author:
    Charles Loomis
